點跟到終點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSpace fantasy 幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔好信官網個開園時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巡遊真係好好玩，隊尾d 人由頭玩到尾</blockquote><br />\n想問下佢幾點開始巡?搵唔倒時間<br />\n淨係見倒有人話下午開始</blockquote><br />\n好似係1410 左右（錯左唔負責）<br />\n上次一點搭九果陣巡遊路線兩邊已經坐滿人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0232c1f99d2d0a98bb56b5cc8c982ad8c7a11407","tid":82900,"uid":37583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔買快証，同工作人員講排單丁會快好多</blockquote><br />\n排單丁一樣排到2046<br />\n利申: 未去過USJ, 但有fd試過自己去排單丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈利入園就排隊1個鐘<br />\n翼龍單丁3個鐘 非單丁4個鐘<br />\nSpiderman 單丁15分鐘<br />\nSpacefantasy 單丁15分鐘。<br />\n侏羅紀單丁即入即玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n親身經驗俾你哋參考"},{"pid":"e1fc38f98d00ad60149b36115b1a6c8bf3c5d50b","tid":82900,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩13-1-17開左5個新館<br />\n哥師拉<br />\n柯南<br />\neva<br />\nmonster hunter<br />\n進擊的巨人<br />\n尋日買左飛同4新館pass<br />\n柯南館係玩密室逃脫，怕唔識日文唔知玩乜，所以冇買5館pass淨買左4pass<br />\n不過香港代理冇呢個pass買，要自己去日本官網買</blockquote><br />\n哥斯拉同eva好唔好玩<br />\n同埋哥斯拉係唔係得晏就場"},{"pid":"870ad31f3df047bda985b20a5f1f24a06f7f4a45","tid":82900,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"大家咁講 姐係買一個fp就得 定係要買唔知幾多個？<br />\n<br />\n利申 就去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6790955035ad68e409aac6092eebca196140b4c","tid":82900,"uid":3900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T04:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家咁講 姐係買一個fp就得 定係要買唔知幾多個？<br />\n<br />\n利申 就去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFP? 你指Express Pass?<br />\n如果你話想無限玩園內設施<br />\n佢同海狗公園一樣係俾你任玩的 (前題係你排到)<br />\n<br />\nExpress有分3款 3,4,7 睇你想玩幾多嘢.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.usj.co.jp/e/ticket/express_pass.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usj.co.jp%2Fe%2Fticket%2Fexpress_pass.html&d=kThX8bkn0l1ex4g4vi8cw0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=1b89679a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.usj.co.jp/e/ticket/express_pass.html</a>"},{"pid":"90c3b52b9323c6ea17e368e3b12adb1ebc7b164a","tid":82900,"uid":58796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩13-1-17開左5個新館<br />\n哥師拉<br />\n柯南<br />\neva<br />\nmonster hunter<br />\n進擊的巨人<br />\n尋日買左飛同4新館pass<br />\n柯南館係玩密室逃脫，怕唔識日文唔知玩乜，所以冇買5館pass淨買左4pass<br />\n不過香港代理冇呢個pass買，要自己去日本官網買</blockquote><br />\n哥斯拉同eva好唔好玩<br />\n同埋哥斯拉係唔係得晏就場</blockquote><br />\n好唔好玩我遲先答倒你，我下星期先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57af99796d6933efe8f1710b8ab1080014c9bdd","tid":82900,"uid":58796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家咁講 姐係買一個fp就得 定係要買唔知幾多個？<br />\n<br />\n利申 就去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFP? 你指Express Pass?<br />\n如果你話想無限玩園內設施<br />\n佢同海狗公園一樣係俾你任玩的 (前題係你排到)<br />\n<br />\nExpress有分3款 3,4,7 睇你想玩幾多嘢.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.usj.co.jp/e/ticket/express_pass.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usj.co.jp%2Fe%2Fticket%2Fexpress_pass.html&d=kThX8bkn0l1ex4g4vi8cw0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=1b89679a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.usj.co.jp/e/ticket/express_pass.html</a></blockquote><br />\n入左官網，右上角語言選日文，會連返去日本果邊官網，會多幾種pass，香港代理冇得賣既<br />\n我都係睇呢個網個購票教學跟住做咁買<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.travelclassroom.net/2016/01/universal-studios-japan.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.travelclassroom.net%2F2016%2F01%2Funiversal-studios-japan.html&d=kThX8bkn0l1ex4g4vi8cw0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3338b261\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.travelclassroom.net/2016/01/universal-studios-japan.html</a>"},{"pid":"030c1f02e12b6ecd2fca7e28e8836903c6b2f496","tid":82900,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"睇黎唔買快證係會排到成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456252b09c8f7e64f64ba8f4808d4e1b5238473e","tid":82900,"uid":59222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T08:29:25.000Z","msg":"上星期閒日去左，買左express 4 包哈利<br />\n朝早哈利normal queue 60mins, 用左express, 唔洗5分鐘排到<br />\n晏就4點幾再排，個牌寫25mins, 實際仲快過朝早用express pass <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他設施基本都唔洗點排，不過我冇玩任何過山車<br />\n<br />\n但我都冇後悔買左express pass既，始終當日人流好難預<br />\n<br />\nPs Hp fans, 用左成千幾2千hkd 買products<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋成個樂團氣氛好好，好多日本妹著到成隻minion咁，男既都有，parade 時大家都好投入<br />\n好開心我玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35be8d519b9e7f02471fe5017f8368075cb04d7d","tid":82900,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇黎唔買快證係會排到成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我舊年summer 去冇快證玩到大部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但真係要排好耐"},{"pid":"9805d6bc7c97976fabc2aa485474ce533090ead1","tid":82900,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"好玩, 值得去. <br />\n日本樂園好多學生研修旅行...排隊都多過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}